**Fiverr**
Fiverr is an online freelance marketplace where individuals and businesses can hire skilled professionals for services like graphic design, programming, writing, marketing, and more.
It works through a “gig” system, where freelancers list services with pricing and clients can browse, compare, and purchase based on their needs and budget.
The platform is widely used for outsourcing tasks, building side income, and accessing global talent quickly without long hiring processes.

Link: https://www.fiverr.com/

