**Flex Jobs**
FlexJobs is a curated job marketplace that focuses on flexible work arrangements like remote, part‑time, freelance, and flexible schedule roles across industries.
All listings are screened for legitimacy, so you won’t run into scams or junk postings common on free job boards.
It’s used by professionals who want trustworthy, quality opportunities without sacrificing flexibility or work‑life balance.

Link: https://www.flexjobs.com/

