**Freelancer**
Freelancer.in is an online freelancing marketplace where businesses and individuals can hire professionals for tasks like software development, data work, design, writing, and marketing.
It works by letting clients post projects and receive bids from freelancers, with built-in tools for communication, project tracking, and secure milestone-based payments.
The platform is widely used for outsourcing work, building freelance careers, and accessing global talent without hiring full-time employees, though user experiences can vary depending on projects and clients.

Link: https://www.freelancer.in/

